{
  "stem": "7282.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if she's going to go out, then she can take the sisters out from there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the, the war-- the war ended.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had a pact, like, everybody-- if you are a Polish citizen from back home, you can go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so her sisters registered to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she went to Kiev.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She went to Kiev having in mind that she can take them out to Kiev.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it's happened that they registered to evacuate from there to Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they received a letter from the sisters that they're going to-- that, that, that they going to be, shall we say, the train there passed Kiev.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they'll be, shall we say, this and this day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If she want to see them, she can come out to Kiev and ask for the number of the train-- and to meet them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then she went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she couldn't find them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they, they left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I received a letter from her that her sisters are in Liegnitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went to Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Liegnitz belonged to Poland then because they divided Poland and Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When the war ended, they, they divided.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that-- the sisters with their husbands are in Liegnitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was stationed in Liegnitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was stationed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I didn't-- she, she sent me the letter after they left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They stayed in Liegnitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the meantime, it's-- came my turn to demobilize from the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they begged me to stay there for another two years in the army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not as-- I mean, like a, a private citizen, you know, to work for them, in, in the army for two years.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They, they gave me a two-, two-month's vacation.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
